text: Federica Rossi (born 7 June 2001) is an Italian tennis player. Rossi has a career high WTA singles ranking of 720 achieved on 31 December 2018. She also has a career high WTA doubles ranking of 686 achieved on 27 May 2019. Rossi made her WTA main draw debut at the 2019 Internazionali Femminili di Palermo in the doubles draw partnering Elisabetta Cocciaretto. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female tennis players Category:People from Sondrio
